com.sap.cloud.sdk.s4hana.datamodel.odata.services

Class DefaultReadProcessOrdersService

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sap.cloud.sdk.s4hana.datamodel.odata.services.DefaultReadProcessOrdersService
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ReadProcessOrdersService

    @Named
public class DefaultReadProcessOrdersService
extends Object
implements ReadProcessOrdersService

    This service enables you to read order headers, items, operations, components, statuses, and production/resource tools (PRTs) belonging to process orders.

    Business Documentation

    Reference: SAP API Business Hub

    Details:

    OData Service:API_PROCESS_ORDERS
    API Version:1
    Communication Scenario:Production Planning Integration (SAP_COM_0104)
    Scope Items:Material Requirements Planning (J44)
